    <cas:Sofa xmi:id="1" sofaNum="1" sofaID="_InitialView" mimeType="text" sofaString="(Whole of Syria, April 2021) The national average price of WFP’s standard reference food basket decreased between March and April 2021 by two percent, reaching SYP 176,471 (USD 71 at the official exchange rate of SYP 2,500/USD). This is the first month-on-month (m-o-m) decrease in the food basket price since August 2020, and it is linked to the improvement in the informal exchange rate by 26 percent between March and April 2021. Eight governorates recorded a decreasing average reference food basket price in April 2021. The highest m-o-m decrease of 17 percent was re-ported in Idleb reaching SYP 183,563, followed by Al-Hasakeh (down 16 percent), reaching SYP 127,870. The remaining six governorates recorded an increasing reference food basket price. The high-est increase of 11 percent was reported in Damas-cus reaching SYP 181,118, followed by Rural Damas-cus (up nine percent) reaching SYP 180,589"/>
    <cas:View sofa="1" members="8 19 24 29 34 39 44 49 62 75 88 101 114 127 140 153 166 179 192 205 218 231 244 257 270 283 296 309 322 335 348 361 374 387 400 413 426 439 452 465 478 491 504 517 530 543 556 569 582 595 608 621 634 647 660 673 686 699 712 725 738 751 764 777 790 803 816 829 842 855 868 881 894 907 920 933 946 959 972 985 998 1011 1024 1037 1050 1063 1076 1089 1102 1115 1128 1141 1154 1167 1180 1193 1206 1219 1232 1245 1258 1271 1284 1297 1310 1323 1336 1349 1362 1375 1388 1401 1414 1427 1440 1453 1466 1479 1492 1505 1518 1531 1544 1557 1570 1583 1596 1609 1622 1635 1648 1661 1674 1687 1700 1713 1726 1739 1752 1765 1778 1791 1804 1817 1830 1843 1856 1869 1882 1895 1908 1921 1934 1947 1960 1973 1986 1999 2012 2025 2038 2051 2064 2077 2090 2103 2116 2129 2142 2155 2168 2181 2194 2207 2259 2264 2220 2230 2225 2235 2240 2297 2302 2307 2338 2343 2333 2362 2367 2372 2401 2391 2396 2420 2425 2452 2437 2447 2442 2471 2497 2502 2584 2521 2526 2531 2536 2541 2546 2551 2276 2283 2290 2326 2269 2252 2245 2312 2319 2348 2355 2377 2384 2413 2406 2476 2483 2490 2430 2457 2464 2514 2507 2589 2596 2603 2624 2570 2577 2610 2617 2556 2563 2631 2638 2634 2641 2645 2658"/>
